quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Qaaf. Mi woo…óndirii Alqur'aanaare teddunde ndeen!"
  50,2,"Si ko woni, …ďe Ňčal…óu ko tawi kon jeertinoowo arii …ďe iw…óo e ma…ď…ďe ; he'efer…ďe …ďen mbi'i: ""∆äuum …óoo ko hu'unde haawniinde."
  50,3,"Kere si min maayii, min ngoontii mbulmbuldi...? ∆äuum …óon ko duttitagol go…ó…óungol noon !"""
  50,4,"GooŇč…óii mi…óen nganndi ko leydi ndin √Īaamata kon e ma…ď…ďe ; hino ka Amen gaa deftere reennde."
  50,5,"Si ko woni, …ďe njeddu goonga kan tuma nde ka arnoo e ma…ď…ďe, hi…ďe e ndeer fiyaaku jil…ďu…óo."
  50,6,"E …ďee ndaaraani kammu ngun dow ma…ď…ďe, ko honno Min mahiri ngun Min cu…óini ngu ; hara per…ói alanaa ngu?"
  50,7,"Leydi ndin kadi, Min mbeerti ndi Min mberlii e mayri pelle, Min pu…óini e mayri kala nooneeji [pu…ói] goo…óu…ói."
  50,8,"fii tasakuyee e waaju wonan'de kala jiyaa…óo duttotoo…óo."
  50,9,"Min njippini kadi ndiyam mbarkinaa…óam ummaade ka kammu, Min pu…óiniri …óam gese e gabbe co√Īetee…óe."
  50,10,"e le…ó…óe tamaro juut…óe gon'dude e piindi fawondirndi,"
  50,11,"ko arsike jeyaa…ďe …ďen. Min nguurnitiri …óam kadi leydi yoorundi. Awa ko noon woni fii ummital ngal."
  50,12,"Ado ma…ď…ďe, yim…ďe nuuhu …ďen, e yim…ďe ∆Āunndu …ďeen e Samuuda'en [fof] f Njedduno,"
  50,13,"e 'Aadi'en, e Fir'awna e musi…ó…ďe Luutu …ďeen."
  50,14,"e yim…ďe fitaare nden, e yim…ďe Tubba' …ďeen. Kala ma…ď…ďe jed…óuno Nulaa…ďe …ďeen, kammbaa am on jojji."
  50,15,"Kere Min ndoŇčkuno fii tagoore ado nde? Ko woni kam…ďe, hi…ďe e ji…ďaare fii tagiteede laawol kesol."
  50,16,"GooŇč…óii Min tagii ne…ó…óaŇčke on, Me…óen nganndi ko woŇčkii makko kin sowinsinirta mo. Ko Minen …ďuri …ďadaade mo e dii …óa…óol (makko) daande ngol."
  50,17,"tuma nde ja…ď…ďoytoo…ďe …ďeen …ói…óo ja…ď…ďoroytoo [golle makko …óeen] √Īaamo e nano, hara hi…ďe njoo…óii."
  50,18,"O wowlataa konngol, si wonaa hino takko makko binndoowo tawaa…óo."
  50,19,"∆äe…ó…óere maayde nden ardi e goonga : ""Ko …óuum wonnnoo ko ndogayno…óaa""."
  50,20,"Wuttee ka alaandu ; ko nden woni √Ďalaande kammbaa ndeen."
  50,21,"WoŇčkii kala ara, hara hiki won'di e coggoowo e ceedotoo…óo."
  50,22,"""GooŇč…óii a laatinoke belsindii…óo e ndee. Min kunci wirngallo maa ngon kisan; gite maa …óeen hannde ko cee…ď…óe""."
  50,23,"Gonndiijo makko on wi'a: ""Ko …óuum …óoo woni ka am …óoo, maandinaa-…óum""."
  50,24,"Bugee ka Jahannama onon …ói…óo, kala jeddu…óo canndallo."
  50,25,"Ka…óoowo mo∆ī∆īere, jaggitoowo, cikkitii…óo,"
  50,26,"on ba…óidu…óo e Allah dewetee…óo goo. Bugee mo ka ndeer lepte ca…ótu…óe""."
  50,27,"Cinndadiijo makko (seytaane) on wi'i: ""Joomi amen, mi bewinaali oo; si ko woni, ko e majjere wo…ó…óunde o wonnoo e mum""."
  50,28,"[Allah] daala : ""Wota on njeddondir ka Am …óoo ! Nde tawnoo Mi ardiniino e mon kammbaa."
  50,29,"Konngol wa…ótitetaake ka am …óoo ; Mi siforaa kadi too√Īoowo jiyaa…ďe …ďen""."
  50,30,"√Ďande Min mbi'anoyta Jahannama o : ""E a heewii?"" Nge wi'a: ""Ko …ďeydee hino woodi?"""
  50,31,"Aljanna on …ďa…ótinanee gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďen, hara wonaa ka wo…ó…ói."
  50,32,"""Ko …óum …óoo woni ko poda…óon, wonan'de kala duttii…óo [e Joomi mun] deenii…óo."
  50,33,"oon kulu…óo Joom Hinaranke oon ka wirnii, o ardi e …ďernde laa…ďunde."
  50,34,"Naatiree mo e jam"". Ko nden woni √Īalaande luttaynde ndeen."
  50,35,"Hino woodani …ďe toon kala ko …ďe faaletee, hara kadi …ďeydaari hino ka Amen."
  50,36,"∆äuu…óii e gire …óen Min kalki ado ma…ď…ďe, ko …ďeen …ďurnoo…ďe doole, …ďeen mbanngorii e leydi ndiin, ndaarugol taw si …ďe ke…ďay laaworde."
  50,37,"Pellet, woni e …óuum, waajo wonan'de kala jom …ďernde, maa tu…óu…óo noppi hara ko tawaa…óo."
  50,38,"GooŇč…óii Min tagii kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, ndeer bal…óe jeegoo, tampere woo he…ďaani Min."
  50,39,"Mu√Ī√Īo e ko …ďe kaalata kon, subbunhinano…óaa Joomi maa ado pu…óal na'ange ngen e ado mutal ngal."
  50,40,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinano…óaa mo e ka battane [julu…óe] farlaa…óe."
  50,41,"He…óo, √Īande noddoowo o noddoyta e nokkuure …ďattiinde,"
  50,42,"√Īande …ďe naniroyta ha'acaango ngon e hoore goonga. Ko ndeen woni √Ďande yaltugol ngol [ka genaale]."
  50,43,"Pellet, ko Monen nguurnata Min mbara, ko ka amen kadi woni ruttorde nde."
  50,44,"√Ďalnde leydi ndiin seekotoo […ďe njaltira] ke√Īagol; ko nde woni moo…ďirde newaniinde Min."
  50,45,"Ko Minen …ďuri anndude ko …ďe kaalata kon. A wonaa dooloowo…ďe. Haray waajor Alqur'aanaare nden, kala kuloowo kammbaa an on."
